#

Lemon Herb Grilled Shrimp Tacos

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

shellfish

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carb

Cuisine:

MexicanAmerican

Course:

mainlunch

Tags:

easyquickgrilledtacos

Description

Fresh and zesty grilled shrimp tacos topped with a vibrant herb sauce, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • shrimp, peeled and deveined: 1 lb
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • dried oregano: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/4 tsp
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • cabbage, shredded: 2 cups
  • fresh cilantro, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • avocado, sliced: 1
